 307:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * The function reads the FCE module disable status (DISS) bit. It returns "true" if
