 323:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * The function asserts the FCE peripheral reset and sets the DISR bit in the CLC
