 352:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * The function sets to the CFG and CRC registers with the FCE configuration and
