 534:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * When the CFG.CCE bit field is set, every time the IR register is written, the
 535:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * LENGTH register is decremented by one until it reaches zero. The hardware monitors
 536:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * the transition of the LENGTH register from 1 to 0 to detect the end of the
 537:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * message and proceed with the comparison of the result register (RES) value with
 538:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * the CHECK register value.
