 555:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * When the ALR bit field is set to 1, every write to the IR register decrements
 556:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * the value of the LENGTH bit field. The LENGTH field shall be reloaded with its
 557:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  * configuration value at the end of the cycle where LENGTH reaches 0.
 558:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_fce.h ****  */
